Package: gphys
Type: Package
Title: Analyse electrophysiology data acquired by Neuromatic / Igor Pro
Version: 0.1
Date: 2011-11-17
Author: Greg Jefferis
Maintainer: Greg Jefferis <jefferis@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides functions to make spike time raster plots for
  data acquired and pre-analysed by the Neuromatic package for Igor Pro. The 
  input data format is a simple text file saved by Igor and could no doubt be
  generated by other spike sorting packages.
  See http://www.neuromatic.thinkrandom.com/ for details on Neuromatic.
Depends: tools
Suggests: IgorR
License: GPL (>= 2)
